        "subject": "LU-10635 ldlm: check if the resource is available before accessing it",
        "message": "LU-10635 ldlm: check if the resource is available before accessing it\n\nThe pointer to the ldlm resource could be null, it will cause panic\nin ldlm_process_plain_lock() as follows:\nBUG: unable to handle kernel NULL pointer dereference at 000000000000001c\nIP: [<ffffffffc11048ce>] ldlm_process_plain_lock+0x6e/0xb30 [ptlrpc]\nCall Trace:\n [<ffffffffc1104860>] ? ldlm_errno2error+0x60/0x60 [ptlrpc]\n [<ffffffffc10ef9db>] ldlm_reprocess_queue+0x13b/0x2a0 [ptlrpc]\n [<ffffffffc10f057d>] __ldlm_reprocess_all+0x14d/0x3a0 [ptlrpc]\n [<ffffffffc10f0b30>] ldlm_reprocess_res+0x20/0x30 [ptlrpc]\n [<ffffffffc0a36bef>] cfs_hash_for_each_relax+0x21f/0x400 [libcfs]\n [<ffffffffc10f0b10>] ? ldlm_lock_downgrade+0x320/0x320 [ptlrpc]\n [<ffffffffc10f0b10>] ? ldlm_lock_downgrade+0x320/0x320 [ptlrpc]\n [<ffffffffc0a39d95>] cfs_hash_for_each_nolock+0x75/0x1c0 [libcfs]\n [<ffffffffc10f0b7c>] ldlm_reprocess_recovery_done+0x3c/0x110 [ptlrpc]\n [<ffffffffc10f17bc>] ldlm_export_cancel_locks+0x11c/0x130 [ptlrpc]\n [<ffffffffc111ada8>] ldlm_bl_thread_main+0x4c8/0x700 [ptlrpc]\n [<ffffffff810c4820>] ? wake_up_state+0x20/0x20\n [<ffffffffc111a8e0>] ? ldlm_handle_bl_callback+0x410/0x410 [ptlrpc]\n [<ffffffff810b099f>] kthread+0xcf/0xe0\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\n\nChange-Id: I60434b0fe476603681c424f85a0ee0ea017f5808\nSigned-off-by: Emoly Liu <emoly.liu@intel.com>\n"
